  MergePatch<T> uses [JsonExtensionData] to capture all incoming JSON
  properties as raw JsonElements, allowing callers to distinguish between
  a property that was absent from the patch and one explicitly set to null.

  Override via tspconfig.yaml:
    options:
      "@massivescale/tsp-aspnetcore-api":
        templates:
          merge-patch: "./templates/merge-patch.hbs"

  ── Template variables ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────

  (none — this template renders a fully static class body)
